title: Shorten Phase 2 and Introduce Phase 3
body:
This is our first [Community Proposal](https://forum.floatprotocol.com/t/end-phase-2-and-introduce-phase-3-proposal/194) by @carebbear / Matija which has been moved to a vote due to the strong community response in the forum.

**Summary:** End Phase 2 at the end of this week (Sunday 28th March 10pm UTC) and introduce Phase 3.

Phase 3 shall last for 6 weeks and only contain the incentivised BANK-ETH SLP pool but not contain any single asset pools. All rewards previously allocated to the second week of Phase 2 (10,500 BANK) are to be distributed only to the BANK-ETH SLP pool over the 6 weeks of Phase 3.

- Week 1 (commencing Sunday 28th March) - 3000 BANK
- Week 2 (commencing Sunday 4th April) - 2500 BANK
- Week 3 (commencing Sunday 11th April) - 2000 BANK
- Week 4 (commencing Sunday 18th April) - 1500 BANK
- Week 5 (commencing Sunday 25th April) - 1000 BANK
- Week 6 (commencing Sunday 2nd May) - 500 BANK
